downloadTitle: Dynamics 365 for Operations on-premises, Enterprise edition Provisioning Guide
downloadDescription: The entity purchasing Dynamics 365 for Operations on-premises, Enterprise edition for production use is required to use a Microsoft Online Services ID. The Microsoft Online Services ID is required to provision and register Microsoft Dynamics 365 for Operations on-premises, Enterprise edition into entity owned hardware and environment.
detailsSection: View the posted document above, and follow the steps to complete the provisioning and registration process.
